reviews.text: Quaint small place. Very busy at times. Quick service. Very flavourful. Small dishes so we can order multiples to try. Good portions for the price. Tasty food.

A traditional Chinese noodle restaurant with a great variety of Chinese menus, ranging from wonton noodles, hotpot congee to steamed fish, from stir-fry to braised pork knuckles. Tiny store with a lot of small tables which make it very crowded during rush hours. Quick service and good food
Very high quality of typical and traditional chinese food, including noodles and congee
Quality of food maintained throughout the years. A nice place for one who wants to try out the Cantonese style dishes and noodles

result.name: 七喜粥麵小廚

reviews.text: 這間七喜粥麵小廚的雲吞麵很好吃，我久不久都會去吃一碗。師傅淥麵的軟硬度很合我心意，麵唔會淋很正👍。 一碗有五粒頗大的雲吞，有肉有蝦但蝦嘅比例多食落好爽口，讚❗🥰
Quaint small place. Very busy at times. Quick service. Very flavourful. Small dishes so we can order multiples to try. Good portions for the price. Tasty food.

一直好味，間間都有水準。 讚！
